channel.title: Logging out problem
channel.description:
I was searching some sources at the sources downloads section, and I found some.
I think I downloaded 5 or 6 sources just to check/test.
Ok, but, one of them, has a problem... I can't log out. I create a new user, then I normally play... When I want to log off, I click on 'Click here to log out' and nothing happens!
Thanks!
